6.8m.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2018/mar/19/electoral-commission-conservatives-spent-lost-majority-2017-election|title=Tories spent \u00a318.5m on election that cost them majority|first=Peter Walker Political|last=correspondent|date=19 March 2018|via=www.theguardian.com}}</ref>\n\n==Endorsements==\n{{Main|Endorsements in the 2017 United Kingdom general election}}\nNewspapers, organisations and individuals endorsed parties or individual candidates for the election. For example, the main national newspapers gave the following endorsements:\n\n===National daily newspapers===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Newspapers\n! colspan=2| Endorsement\n! Notes\n! 2017 circulation (June)<ref name=\"DP\">{{cite news |url=https://www.pressgazette.co.uk/daily-mail-and-sun-launch-front-page-attacks-on-corbyn-as-fleet-street-lines-up-behind-theresa-may/ |title=Daily Mail and Sun launch front-page attacks on Corbyn as Fleet Street lines up behind Theresa May |last=Ponsford |first=Dominic |date=7 June 2017 |work=[[Press Gazette]]}}</ref>\n! Link\n|-\n| ''[[Daily Express]]''\n| style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative Party]]\n|\n| 386,297\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=VOTE MAY OR WE FACE DISASTER: It's time for patriotic realism NOT socialist indulgence |url=http://www.express.co.uk/comment/expresscomment/813903/general-election-2017-Conservatives-Theresa-May-UK-campaign-Daily-Express |website=Daily Express |date=7 June 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Daily Mail]]''\n| style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative Party]]\n|\n| 1,454,073\n|<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/jun/03/which-parties-are-the-uk-press-backing-in-the-general-election |title=Which parties are the UK press backing in the general election? |last=McKee |first=Ruth |work=The Guardian |date=3 June 2017 |accessdate=13 June 2017}}</ref>\n|-\