 She's Coming Out\" teleplay by Albert Torres\n*\"Honeymoon's Over\" teleplay by Sasha Stroman\n\n==Production==\n===Development===\nIn November 2018, it was announced that an adaptation of the series was being developed by Dean Georgaris and [[David Frankel]] through Keshet Studios and [[Universal Television]] for [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]. The series is one of two collaborations between Georgaris and Universal for the 2019\u201320 season, along with ''[[Bluff City Law]]'' for [[NBC]]'s fall schedule.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/abc-the-baker-and-the-beauty-pilot-israeli-format-dean-georgaris-1202544051/|title=ABC Orders 'The Baker And The Beauty' Based On Israeli Format In Second Pilot Pickup For Dean Georgaris This Season|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|last2=Andreeva|first2=Nellie|date=2019-01-28|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-06-10}}</ref> Georgaris and Frankel are set to write and direct, respectively, and both will executive produce alongside [[Avi Nir]], [[Alon Shtruzman]], [[Peter Traugott]], and Rachel Kaplan.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/10/baker-and-the-beauty-romantic-comedy-based-on-israeli-format-from-dean-georgaris-david-frankel-set-at-abc-1202485265/|title='Baker And The Beauty' Romantic Comedy Based On Israeli Format Set At ABC From Dean Georgaris, David Frankel & Keshet|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=October 18, 2018|accessdate=November 9, 2018}}</ref> In January 2019 ABC ordered the adaptation to pilot.<ref>[https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/abc-the-baker-and-the-beauty-1203121008/ ABC Orders Pilot for Drama \u2018The Baker and The Beauty\u2019 Based on Israeli Series] Variety. 28 January 2019</ref> On May 11, 2019, ABC green-lighted the series.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/05/the-baker-and-the-beauty-israeli-format-dean-georgaris-abc-series-order-1202612578/|title='The Baker And The Beauty' Gets ABC Series Order As Dean Georgaris Scores Double|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|first2=Denise|last2=Petski|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=May 11, 2019|accessdate=May 11, 2019}}</ref> A few days later, it was announced that the series would premiere as a [[mid-season replacement]] in the spring of 2020.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/05/abc-fall-2019-20-schedule-upfronts-new-shows-the-rookie-mixed-ish-emergence-cobie-smulders-1202614248|title=ABC Fall 2019-20 Schedule: Very Few Changes, 'The Rookie' Moves To Sunday, 'American Housewife' To Friday|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=from Deadline Hollywood|date=May 14, 2019|accessdate=May 14, 2019}}</ref> On January 8, 2020, it was reported that the series was set to premiere on April 6, 2020.<ref name=\"SeriesPremiereDate\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/midseason-moves-shark-tank-american-housewife-baker-and-the-beauty-premiere-date-tca-1202824384/|title=Midseason Moves For ABC's 'Shark Tank' & 'American Housewife'; 'Baker And The Beauty' Gets Premiere Date \u2013 TCA|work=Deadline Hollywood|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=January 8, 2020|accessdate=January 8, 2020}}</ref> On January 29, 2020, the premiere date was moved to April 13, 2020.<ref name=\"Premiere Date Change\">{{cite web|title=ABC Invites You to the Ultimate Date Night on Monday, April 13|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2020/01/29/abc-invites-you-to-the-ultimate-date-night-on-monday-april-13-124412/20200129abc02/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=January 29, 2020}}</ref>\n\n===Casting===\nIn February 2019, it was announced that [[Carlos G\u00f3mez (actor)|Carlos Gomez]], [[Lisa Vidal]] and [[Dan Bucatinsky]] had been cast in the pilot's lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/the-baker-and-the-beauty-carlos-gomez-lisa-vidal-dan-bucatinsky-cast-abc-comedy-pilot-1202567280/|title='The Baker And The Beauty': Carlos Gomez, Lisa Vidal & Dan Bucatinsky Cast In ABC Comedy Pilot|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|first2=Denise|last2=Petski|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=February 28, 2019|accessdate=May 12, 2019}}</ref> Alongside the pilot's order announcement, in March 2019 it was reported that [[Nathalie Kelley]], [[Victor Rasuk]], [[Michelle Veintimilla]] and [[David Del Rio]] had joined the cast.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/nathalie-kelley-star-the-baker-and-the-beauty-abc-comedy-pilot-1202569310/|title=Nathalie Kelley To Star In 'The Baker And The Beauty' ABC Romantic Comedy Pilot|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|first2=Denise|last2=Petski|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=March 4, 2019|accessdate=May 12, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/the-baker-and-the-beauty-victor-rasuk-star-abc-romantic-comedy-pilot-1202570274/|title='The Baker And The Beauty': Victor Rasuk To Star In ABC Romantic Comedy Pilot|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=March 6, 2019|accessdate=May 12, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/abc-pilots-united-we-fall-stumptown-baker-and-the-beauty-leslie-odom-jr-jason-michael-snow-adrian-martinez-michelle-veintimilla-alexis-fields-1202573118/|title=ABC Pilots 'United We Fall', 'Stumptown', 'Baker & The Beauty' & Leslie Odom Jr. Comedy Add To Cast|first=Denise|last=Petski|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=March 11, 2019|accessdate=May 12, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/christian-borle-abc-until-the-wedding-david-del-rio-the-baker-and-the-beauty-1202576213/|title=Christian Borle Joins ABC's 'Until The Wedding'; David Del Rio In 'The Baker And The Beauty'|first=Denise|last=Petski|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=March 15, 2019|accessdate=May 12, 2019}}</ref> In September 2019, [[Georgina Reilly]] was cast in a recurring role.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/maria-gabriela-de-faria-fox-a-moody-christmas-the-baker-the-beauty-casts-georgina-reilly-1202747019/|title=Maria Gabriela de Faria Joins Fox's 'A Moody Christmas'; 'The Baker & The Beauty' Casts Georgina Reilly|first1=Dominic|last1=Patten|first2=Denise|last2=Petski|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=September 30, 2019|accessdate=September 30, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Filming===\nThe pilot was filmed in [[Atlanta]] while rest of the series was filmed in [[Puerto Rico]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://popculture.com/tv-shows/2020/04/13/baker-beauty-lisa-vidal-recounts-extreme-conditions-filming-connected-cast-exclusive/|title='The Baker and the Beauty': Lisa Vidal Recounts How Extreme Conditions While Filming Connected the Cast (Exclusive)|first=Stephanie|last=Downs|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=April 13, 2020|accessdate=April 14, 2020}}</ref>\n==Reception==\n<!--===Critical response===-->\n===Ratings===\n{{Television episode ratings\n| width     = 99\n| noshare   = y\n\n| title1    = [[#ep1|Pilot]]\n| date1     = April 13, 2020\n| rs1       = 0.5\n| viewers1  = 2.66<ref name=\"1.01\"/>\n| dvr1      = \n| dvrv1     =\n| total1    =\n| totalv1   = \n<!--\n| title2    = [[#ep2|Ruin My Life]]\n| date2     = April 20, 2020\n| rs2       = \n| viewers2  = \n| dvr2      = \n| dvrv2     =\n| total2    = \n| totalv2   = \n\n| title3    = [[#ep3|Get Carried Away]]\n| date3     = April 27, 2020\n| rs3       = \n| viewers3  = \n| dvr3      = \n| dvrv3     =\n| total3    =\n| totalv3   = \n\n| title4    = [[#ep4|]]\n| date4     =\n| rs4       =\n| viewers4  = \n| dvr4      =\n| dvrv4     = \n| total4    = \n| totalv4   =\n\n| title5    = [[#ep5|]]\n| date5     =\n| rs5       = \n| viewers5  = \n| dvr5      = \n| dvrv5     = \n| total5    = \n| totalv5   =\n\n| title6    = [[#ep6|]]\n| date6     = \n| rs6       =\n| viewers6  = \n| dvr6      =\n| dvrv6     =\n| total6    = \n| totalv6   =\n\n| title7    = [[#ep7|]]\n| date7     = \n| rs7       = \n| viewers7  = \n| dvr7      =\n| dvrv7     = \n| total7    =\n| totalv7   = \n\n| title8    = [[#ep8|]]\n| date8     =\n| rs8       =\n| viewers8  = \n| dvr8      =\n| dvrv8     =\n| total8    =\n| totalv8   = \n\n| title9    = [[#ep9|]]\n| date9     =\n| rs9       =\n| viewers9  = \n